data.title: It’s December 1st Folks! ❄️☃️🎄I’m filming a little something for Richard Curtis to celebrate Love Actually. ❤️ The nights are drawing in...
data.meta_description: 37K likes, 749 comments - martinemccutcheon on December 1, 2023: "It’s December 1st Folks! ❄️☃️🎄I’m filming a little something for Richard Curtis to celebrate Love Actually. ❤️ The nights are drawing in and it’s crispy cold out there! If you haven’t already, it’s time to watch it! If the movie doesn’t get you feeling festive, nothing will! 😁🤷🏻‍♀️❤️🎄💫 After all these years, I STILL can’t believe my ultimate dream of working with Hugh and Richard came true. (Mic drop😆) #christmastime #filming🎬 #loveactually❤️ #acelebration #stillpinchingmyself #hughandi #londonpremiere #adorehimactually".
